Apparently nobody wants to offer up any information on Gharzak.  I'm gonna camp him this Friday until I find him or fall asleep at the keyboard.  Any info I can offer after its over I'll post here and I ask anyone who posted here requesting info and has gotten it elsewhere to please post it so the others of us can get in on the slaying.<BR>
