<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Kuuin</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-04 01:50:03</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>First of all Grazhak does not turn invisible, more idiotic nonsense. He is a very rare spawn in a place that many people don't hang out. If Grazhak was a rare spawn in a place like Oasis he'd probably show up 3 times a day or more because everything is constantly being killed there. Not many people hang out in that area of Rathe Mountains therefore his placeholders are rarely killed. I guarantee if you just set away a few nights and do nothing but clear placeholders he would eventually spawn.<BR>
<BR>
As far as level he was VERY green at 50. 2 starfires pretty much wiped him out which says he has a little over 1200hp. He didn't have the axe with him so he might be tougher with it, especially if the proc goes off and he gets the shield skin. If anyone wants a screenshot of this guy I can send it to someone or post it somewhere on the net.</font></td></tr></table>
